    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288210/extras/e92bac31f95f319c53875e181459891b.poster.avif?t=1772470485\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288210/extras/e92bac31f95f319c53875e181459891b.webm?t=1772470485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288210/extras/e92bac31f95f319c53875e181459891b.mp4?t=1772470485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Super Meat Boy 3D》</strong>是一款硬核平台跳跃游戏，你将扮演一团卡通肉块，努力从装在罐子里的邪恶礼服胎儿手中拯救你的绷带女友——这次是 3D 版哦！<br><br>咱们的肉肉英雄将飞檐走壁，上刀山跨锯海，穿过摇摇欲坠的洞穴，淌过阵阵腐臭的垃圾池，牺牲自我来拯救他的落难少女——3D 版的！    <br>    <br><strong>《Super Meat Boy 3D》</strong>完美继承了经典复古游戏中备受推崇的老派难度，并将其简化为纯粹直接绝不废话拼直觉反应的平台跳跃体验。游戏难度将从困难一路提升到折磨，肉肉哥也将一路过关斩将，在熊熊燃烧的密林、堆满人类废料的巨大垃圾场和生产陷阱的高科技熔炉中勇往直前——全部都是 3D 版！<br>    <br>如果这么多关卡都不够过瘾，我们还准备了史诗级 BOSS 战和海量的可解锁秘密——通通 3D 版！<br><br>  <br>  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288210/extras/9415e608de81774f453e17f5415ed2a1.avif?t=1772470485\" width=616 height=105 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >极度硬核的精准平台动作玩法</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >残酷但合理的关卡设计，让你痛并快乐着</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boss 战</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >难度逆天的黑暗世界关卡，虐你虐到怀疑人生</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏原声音乐。某吉他店店员曾评论道：“爱买买，不买滚。不然我们就报警了。”</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3D</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288210/extras/97238889a904d9fec5ae1bf7bc137ac4.poster.avif?t=1772470485\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288210/extras/97238889a904d9fec5ae1bf7bc137ac4.webm?t=1772470485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288210/extras/97238889a904d9fec5ae1bf7bc137ac4.mp4?t=1772470485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
